metadata.description: **PUBLIC MINTING IS LIVE NOW: https://basc.club.**  *Become a BASC member for only .09 ETH.*  BASC is a set of 10,000 Bored Ape NFTs inspired by the original BAYC collection.  Each colorful, AI-pixelated NFT is a one-of-a-kind collectible that lives on the Ethereum blockchain.  Your Superpixel Bored Ape also serves as your Club membership card, granting you access to exclusive benefits for Club members.
